Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Street crime fears
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkqd
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Apr 1985
As the Bernhard Goetz trial nears, how far should self-defence go when it comes to street crime? This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less